| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0746 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 24fc3b3f-eefa-5f1e-a260-26005f66b98b"
